rm_of_Swords-Chapter_51\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 51\">Chapter 51</a>, Catelyn VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Samwell II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Jaime III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_46\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a>, A Ghost in Winterfell.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_57\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 57\">Chapter 57</a>, Tyrion XI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rssm2997.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rssm2997.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <i><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/2997\">Asshai.com Forum Chat</a></i> (July 27, 2008).</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403200313\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.063 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.096 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1439/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9288/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5311/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1670/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 10603/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.020/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.25 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   74.074      1 -total\n 45.68%   33.836     17 Template:Ref\n 38.66%   28.639      1 Template:For\n 31.88%   23.618     17 Template:Ref/core\n  6.20%    4.594      1 Template:References\n  5.46%    4.043      1 Template:Date\n  4.16%    3.085      1 Template:Lyrics\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:1419-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403200313 and revision id 323615\n -->\n",
